snippet.title: ARCHWIZARD v0.28 Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
ARCHWIZARD is an arena FPS
1 hp × 60 spells you can cast anytime
emergent combat puzzles
post-power-fantasy journey

https://store.steampowered.com/app/955010/ARCHWIZARD/

Trailer music contains tracks: Shadows And Dust by Scott Buckley and Creepy Dark Atmosphere by Universfield
